            <p>This is a calculated metric that expresses the proportion of stolen property that has been successfully
                recovered in relation to the total value of property stolen. The percentage provides insights into the
                efficiency of law enforcement efforts in solving and closing cases related to property crimes. A higher
                percentage indicates a more successful recovery rate.</p>
            <p>These metrics are crucial for law enforcement agencies, policymakers, and the public to understand the
